{
  "id": "665d070b2269d9001cbc9d80",
  "title": "各自のネイティブ言語で同時に議論できる箇条書き翻訳システム",
  "created": 1717372683,
  "updated": 1717397803,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "665d070b2269d9001cbc9d80",
      "text": "各自のネイティブ言語で同時に議論できる箇条書き翻訳システム",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1717372683,
      "updated": 1717372683
    },
    {
      "id": "665d070b6eb4060000d78599",
      "text": "from [2024/06/01]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1717372683,
      "updated": 1717372683
    },
    {
      "id": "665d070b6eb4060000d7859b",
      "text": "これは、、[blu3mo.icon]さんの[非対称なエディタ]に似たものを感じる[inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1717372683,
      "updated": 1717372699
    },
    {
      "id": "665d070b6eb4060000d7859c",
      "text": " [各自のネイティブ言語で同時に議論できる箇条書き翻訳システム by shokai | プロポーザル | builderscon 2024 #builderscon - fortee.jp https://fortee.jp/builderscon-2024/proposal/84c6c188-4f15-4775-9ff2-749ddbb445aa]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1717372683,
      "updated": 1717372683
    },
    {
      "id": "665d070b6eb4060000d7859d",
      "text": " ほんとだ！……って[shokai.icon]さんじゃん！[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1717372683,
      "updated": 1717372683
    },
    {
      "id": "665d070b6eb4060000d7859e",
      "text": " [Scrapboxの翻訳機能]の話っぽいな",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1717372683,
      "updated": 1717372683
    },
    {
      "id": "665d070b6eb4060000d7859f",
      "text": "  でも今の実装だと同時に編集にはならないから、何か新しい機能なのかな？[inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1717372683,
      "updated": 1717372683
    },
    {
      "id": "665d070b6eb4060000d785a0",
      "text": "   今の実装は行の下に翻訳が出てるだけと理解してる",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1717372683,
      "updated": 1717372683
    },
    {
      "id": "665d070b6eb4060000d785a1",
      "text": "  Scrapbox自体が同時編集可能ということでは。[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1717372683,
      "updated": 1717372683
    },
    {
      "id": "665d070b6eb4060000d785a2",
      "text": "   下に表示される翻訳はScrapboxの本文ではなく個々のユーザのネイティブ言語だから「各自のネイティブ言語で書いて各自のネイティブ言語の翻訳を読む」ことができるということなのでは？[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1717372683,
      "updated": 1717372683
    },
    {
      "id": "665d070b6eb4060000d785a3",
      "text": "   あーなるほど、深読みしすぎたか[inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1717372683,
      "updated": 1717372683
    },
    {
      "id": "665d070b6eb4060000d785a4",
      "text": "   あーそういうことなのか。Start Translation舐めてた[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1717372683,
      "updated": 1717372683
    },
    {
      "id": "665d070b6eb4060000d785a5",
      "text": "   \t勝手に「いやページ中には単一の言語（日本語なら日本語だけ）しか書けないから同時編集は厳しい」と思い込んでた",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1717372683,
      "updated": 1717372683
    },
    {
      "id": "665d070b6eb4060000d785a6",
      "text": "   interesting feature[blu3mo.icon]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1717372683,
      "updated": 1717372683
    },
    {
      "id": "665d070b6eb4060000d785a7",
      "text": "   the difference between shokai-san's and mine:",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1717372683,
      "updated": 1717372683
    },
    {
      "id": "665d070b6eb4060000d785a8",
      "text": "    with cosense, a line written in one language cannot be edited by another. ",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1717372683,
      "updated": 1717372683
    },
    {
      "id": "665d070b6eb4060000d785a9",
      "text": "    on the other hand, with [blu3mo.icon]'s editor, everything written in any language can be edited in any other language.",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1717372683,
      "updated": 1717372683
    },
    {
      "id": "665d070b6eb4060000d785aa",
      "text": "    　実際上は他の人が書いた行を編集することはあまりないので困らなさそう[yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1717372683,
      "updated": 1717372683
    },
    {
      "id": "665d070b6eb4060000d785ab",
      "text": "    　 [脱線.icon][\" なので困らない？]だと[\" , so why bother?]という変な訳になったので[\" 困らなさそう]に書き換えた",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1717372683,
      "updated": 1717372683
    },
    {
      "id": "665d070b6eb4060000d785ac",
      "text": "    　 　この行も変な訳だ…",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1717372683,
      "updated": 1717372683
    },
    {
      "id": "665d070b6eb4060000d785ad",
      "text": "    　 　[拡張記法]を使うと変になる可能性？",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1717372683,
      "updated": 1717372683
    },
    {
      "id": "665d070b6eb4060000d785ae",
      "text": "  \t\t\t\t現時点でも結構まちがった翻訳出ちゃう[はるひ.icon]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1717372683,
      "updated": 1717372683
    },
    {
      "id": "665d070b6eb4060000d785af",
      "text": "    however, [blu3mo.icon]'s editor is still under development and texts cannot be synced in realtime.",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1717372683,
      "updated": 1717372683
    },
    {
      "id": "665d070b6eb4060000d785b0",
      "text": "    [blu3mo.icon]'s is also cost-inefficient since it passes the entire content to the LLM everytime we sync between languages.",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1717372683,
      "updated": 1717372683
    },
    {
      "id": "665d070b6eb4060000d785b1",
      "text": "     変更のあった行のみ渡すシステムを構築してみてはいかがでしょうか[bsahd.icon]",
      "userId": "661b6e882a96e9002371b3c2",
      "created": 1717372683,
      "updated": 1717397803
    },
    {
      "id": "665d070b6eb4060000d785b2",
      "text": "\t面白そう、俺もキャッチアップしよ[sta.icon]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1717372683,
      "updated": 1717372683
    },
    {
      "id": "665d070b6eb4060000d785b3",
      "text": "\t面白そうってsounds interestingって表現するのか～[/icons/知見.icon][takker.icon]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1717372683,
      "updated": 1717372683
    },
    {
      "id": "665d070b6eb4060000d785b4",
      "text": "\t sound/look/seemなどの知覚動詞は使える範囲が日本語より広くておもしろい[wogikaze.icon][takker.icon]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1717372683,
      "updated": 1717372683
    },
    {
      "id": "665d070b6eb4060000d785b5",
      "text": "\t海外の人と同時編集してみたいな～[yosider.icon][inajob.icon][cak.icon]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1717372683,
      "updated": 1717372683
    },
    {
      "id": "665d070b6eb4060000d785b6",
      "text": "\t\t8月中ばに[/plurality-japanese/Facing the Ocean]とかいうものがありますがどうですか[nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1717372683,
      "updated": 1717372683
    },
    {
      "id": "665d070b6eb4060000d785b7",
      "text": "\tXのPost翻訳機能も似たようなものな気がしてきた[inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1717372683,
      "updated": 1717372683
    },
    {
      "id": "665d61e332ef920000976c0e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ca094b00af7b0001732ef92",
      "created": 1717395889,
      "updated": 1717395910
    },
    {
      "id": "665d61e332ef920000976c10",
      "text": "\t[https://youtu.be/LYHEuj5gjf4?t=1002 「CHI2024」の参加報告会 #29 - YouTube]",
      "userId": "5ca094b00af7b0001732ef92",
      "created": 1717395890,
      "updated": 1717395908
    },
    {
      "id": "665d61e332ef920000976c0f",
      "text": "\t\tここらへんで似たような話をしていた気がした[dokudami.icon]",
      "userId": "5ca094b00af7b0001732ef92",
      "created": 1717395890,
      "updated": 1717395922
    },
    {
      "id": "665d621332ef920000976c12",
      "text": "\t\t\tアクセシビリティを高めるために字幕を用意しているのみだった（ちょっと違うか）",
      "userId": "5ca094b00af7b0001732ef92",
      "created": 1717395938,
      "updated": 1717396090
    },
    {
      "id": "665d62ad32ef920000976c14",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t議論したいという方向性的には同じ？",
      "userId": "5ca094b00af7b0001732ef92",
      "created": 1717396091,
      "updated": 1717396105
    },
    {
      "id": "665d628732ef920000976c13",
